{"word":"ποῦ","slug":"ποῦ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ποῦ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ interrog.\">interrog.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>, direct or indirect, expressing interest in position of someone/<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> <b>where(?)<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of place, without verb of motion <b>where(?), at which place(?)<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> direct: <b><a href='B:470 2:2'>Mt 2:2</a>; <a href='B:470 26:17'>26:17</a>; <a href='B:480 14:12'>Mk 14:12</a>, <a href='B:480 14:14'>14</a>; <a href='B:490 8:25'>Lk 8:25</a>; <a href='B:490 17:17'>17:17</a>, <a href='B:490 17:37'>37</a>; <a href='B:500 1:38'>J 1:38</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in J<b>; <a href='B:520 3:27'>Ro 3:27</a>; <a href='B:530 1:20'>1 Cor 1:20</a>; <a href='B:530 12:17'>12:17</a>; <a href='B:530 15:55'>15:55</a>; <a href='B:550 4:15'>Gal 4:15</a>; <a href='B:670 4:18'>1 Pt 4:18</a>; <a href='B:680 3:4'>2 Pt 3:4</a>; <a href='B:730 2:13'>Rv 2:13</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> indirect: <b><a href='B:470 2:4'>Mt 2:4</a>; <a href='B:480 15:47'>Mk 15:47</a>; <a href='B:500 1:39'>J 1:39</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in J<b>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a></el> (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐχ\">οὐχ</a></el>) <el>ἔχειν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ποῦ\">ποῦ</a></el> have no place (to accomplish <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>) <b><a href='B:470 8:20'>Mt 8:20</a>; <a href='B:490 9:58'>Lk 9:58</a>; <a href='B:490 12:17'>12:17</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of place, with verb of motion <b>where(?), to what place(?), whither(?)<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> direct: <b><a href='B:500 7:35'>J 7:35</a>; <a href='B:500 13:36'>13:36</a>; <a href='B:500 16:5'>16:5</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> indirect: <b><a href='B:500 3:8'>3:8</a>; <a href='B:500 8:14'>8:14</a>; <a href='B:500 9:12'>9:12</a>; <a href='B:500 12:35'>12:35</a>; <a href='B:500 14:5'>14:5</a>; <a href='B:650 11:8'>Hb 11:8</a>; <a href='B:690 2:11'>1 J 2:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πότος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πού\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}